Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku menjadi center,\Ndatanglah ke rumahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau layanan kebersihan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak bisa ambil sif lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, mungkin staf lain yang pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Njangan kemari dan buang waktumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk apa kulakukan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika menurutmu Tamon akan menang,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau bisa bertaruh denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau menurutmu dia juga akan kalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Tuan Fukuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kuberi tahu kau tak boleh\Nbicara seperti itu padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lupakan kesepakatan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habislah aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena bertaruh tanpa bertanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dengan ucapannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak bisa bilang "Tamon akan kalah"\Nmeski bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan diambil hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lakukan yang terbaik\Nsesuai tempo Tuan Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa kehilanganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya. Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Fujita menugaskanku\Nurus pekerjaan rumah di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa aku bekerja di tempat lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terlalu ceroboh. Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat ini sangat lembap juga salahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan beli pelembap udara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk membantumu menang,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tolong beri tahu jika ada yang bisa kubantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan lakukan yang terbaik\Ndengan pekerjaan rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini teh jelaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu ingin jadi idola sejak kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga sudah bekerja keras untuk itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun aku juga menyayangi penggemarku,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak pernah mencintai seseorang\Nsecara khusus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya apa itu "cinta"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya menyukaimu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi perasaan itu juga agak berbeda\Ndari cinta biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mau pergi ke festival bersamaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon dan aku akan ke festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika itu Festival Tamon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mengadakannya di benakku\N365 hari dalam setahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk nyanyikan lagu patah hati,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku harus tahu apa itu cinta lebih dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku harus pergi ke festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat kembang api naik dan memudar,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu menerangi langit lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang-orang berkumpul di sana
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- untuk temukan cinta sejati.\N- Aku senang datang bersamamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa pertemuan baru menanti\N- Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- atau perpisahan?\N- Tunggu, ini salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tempat suci pasangan sepanjang sejarah.\N- Pembohong. Kau suka wanita itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Festival Musim Panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin pergi ke sana\Nuntuk melihat apa itu cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memenangkan babak kedua\NPertarungan Posisi Center!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jika aku terobos masuk ke pesta\Nmakan malam memesona sendirian,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku pasti akan terbakar\Noleh antusiasme semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membayangkan itu membuatku\Nkehilangan keberanian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari mana kau dapat\Nsemua informasi festival itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Spesialis cinta
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memberitahuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Spesialis cinta…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Kinoshita, mau ikut denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya penggemar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa aku pergi\Nke festival bersamamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal seperti itu cuma khayalanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kubilang aku akan berusaha membantu,\Ntapi aku sungguh minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Maafkan aku…\N- Utage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus pergi ke festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya kau
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang bisa kumintai tolong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamu hari ini
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah perwakilan aktor Jepang\Nyang baru-baru ini memperluas
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kariernya ke luar negeri\Ndan populer di mana-mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aktor itu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toshikazu Sakaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga dikenal di industri ini\Nsebagai suami penyayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Istrinya juga penyanyi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasangan harmonis ini
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}masih aktif\Ndi garis depan industri hiburan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}putra mereka juga menjadi topik hangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia Ouri Sakaguchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang debut sebagai penyanyi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan aktif di industri ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seluruh keluarga itu\Nadalah selebritas terkenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Penggemar atau orang industri,\N- Pak Sakaguchi bilang meski sibuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- bahkan yang tak tertarik padaku,\N- dia masih hargai waktu keluarga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- selama mereka di sisiku,\N- Kali ini, kita akan menggali
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- tatapan mereka berubah sedikit.\N- teknik manajemen waktu rahasianya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}wanita itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tetap pergi semalam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sombong sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, belikan topeng itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena Tamon bilang dia harus datang,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan coba membantu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dalam perjalanan mencari cinta ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku pembantunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga. Bukankah ini\Nkencan enam orang sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ini bagian dari tugasku.\N- Rasanya sangat muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rambutmu hitam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini wig? Terlihat alami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meletakkan kantong kertas di kepala\Nakan halangi penglihatanku,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuatku sulit jalan di malam hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untungnya, dia dalam kondisi Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dia dalam kondisi Ikihara,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kembang api akan meledak di benakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa wanita itu di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Mungkinkah mereka\N- Kalau begitu, ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- berpacaran?\N- Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih ada waktu sebelum kembang api.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,\Nmari kita lihat kiosnya dahulu…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta. Di mana cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panas sekali. Di mana sebenarnya cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan biarkan siapa pun\Nmelaporkan Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panas sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa panas ini
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}juga berasal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari pasangan di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa itu hanya suhu luar ruangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak sempat memberitahumu tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yukata ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat di sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Pria itu menunjukkan sisi kerennya\N- Hei, bukankah itu berlebihan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- kepada gadis di sampingnya.\N- Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar… Luar biasa! Selamat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibandingkan memenangkan tiket konser,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ini mudah sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sengaja menghindari wajahmu\Nsaat mengenainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika pada akhirnya aku tak menemukannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukankah aku cuma datang\Nuntuk memberi makan nyamuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang introver sepertiku seharusnya\Ntak datang ke tempat begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gatal, menakutkan, panas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau selalu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengenai hati penggemarmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau adalah Cupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, kau adalah sniper cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, jangan menyerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti bisa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memahami esensi cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan lakukan yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya apa hubungan mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Pasangan berbagi takoyaki.\N- Ini, Taku. Buka mulutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa itu cinta?\N- Ini lezat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini… cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu takoyaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin melakukan yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah. Buka mulutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jarak itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka sungguh pacaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar atau tidak?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, jangan terpisah. Pegang tanganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa… Apa ini…\N- Lidahmu merah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dunia tempat Tamon hanya orang biasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakimu sakit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tak ada orang biasa di dunia ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otakku sedang karnaval.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku tak bisa fokus mencari cinta!\N- Nona Kinoshita, kau tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf jika aku otaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Kau pasti begini
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebab ada masalah\Ndengan persepsiku soal cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan beli minuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku biasanya bicara seolah paham,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku hanya otaku idola.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu sulit bagiku melihat Tamon
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebagai orang biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sama sekali tak tahu\Nmereka pacaran atau tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyebalkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sendirian di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bicara denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap Nona Utage suka ramune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini… Yukata ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak… Dia bukan pacarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami hanya berteman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, tak punya pacar sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya kubilang tak tahu apa itu cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mungkin merayu gadis yang salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah ada banyak gadis manis lainnya\Ndi sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau cocok
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memakai yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tiba-tiba sangat lembut\Nsehingga aku juga merasa aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan bicara dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pacarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu… Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau bilang begitu\Nuntuk menyingkirkan pria itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi wajahmu…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana jika dia tahu kau Tamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga punya sentimen yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sangat cocok
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memakai yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena tak memberitahumu lebih awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi meski aku memujimu,\Nkau mungkin pikir itu seram.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena ciptakan fenomena supernatural!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini… Aku sangat senang, sungguh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau jelas terkejut!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak terbiasa dipuji,\Njadi, aku terkejut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}meski hanya sesaat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pada saat itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon benar-benar seperti orang biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk tahu makna cinta,\Nkami datang ke Festival Musim Panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku mencoba pahami cinta\Ndengan meniru orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah tenang,\Naku sadar betapa bodohnya itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alih-alih hidup begini\Ndan terima ejekan orang,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku lebih baik mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya akan tinggalkan\Nsejarah kelam jika hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sudah depresi sejak awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu emosi yang kau rasakan\Nsaat memikirkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana Tuan Suram\Nbisa beralih ke kepribadian seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tak ada waktu\Nuntuk memikirkan hal ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus mencari cara\Nuntuk menghibur Tuan Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa cinta benar-benar ada?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja. Tamon bilang cinta itu ada!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku sudah sadar\Nbahwa aku tak bisa menirunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, biasanya aku tak bergaul\Ndengan orang seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat iri\Ndengan kehidupan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maka jangan lakukan\Nyang tak biasa kita lakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagimu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ini juga hari libur yang berharga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana jika kita menikmatinya dahulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lupakan soal jadi atasan\Ndan pembantu untuk saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita berteman saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kurasa aku menarik hatinya.\N- Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak dahulu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang bisa membuatku terbuka\Ncuma noda di dinding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya kata teman\Nterlalu terang untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon, apa sebenarnya yang kau alami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku terlalu terburu-buru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ulat, tapi ingin terbang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alih-alih ulat,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"malaikat jatuh tanpa sayap"\Nlebih cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong ubah kalimatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya malaikat jatuh,\Ntapi ingin terbang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku panggil Nyonya Kinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah orang yang lebih dekat\Ndaripada orang lain, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nkurasa aku harus lebih menghormatimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kusangka ini akan terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu akan buatku sedikit gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Disebut nyonya oleh dewa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu terlalu aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, orang-orang memanggilmu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman-temanku memanggilku Utage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau lebih tua dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panggil saja Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa memanggilmu\Ndengan nama depanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kau panggil aku Sampah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan aku memanggilmu Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kino…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak perlu memaksakan diri.\NPanggil aku sesukamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kau Ikihara,\Npanggil aku dengan nama depanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uta…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suram, cepat kemari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo menari bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon selalu bekerja keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski hanya sebentar,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin dia jadi murid SMA biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, biarkan aku menjadi temannya\Nuntuk saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya untuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan membenciku…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa, jangan gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika Tuan Suram adalah murid SMA biasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin dia akan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, tanganku penuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jika menetes, yukatamu akan kotor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepalaku sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya aku yang minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah hampir waktunya untuk kembang api.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada tempat rahasia di dekat sini.\NAyo ke sana untuk menonton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika di sini, kau boleh melepas topengmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panas sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini warna rambutnya yang biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa lebih tenang lihat warna ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mengecat rambutmu\Nselama acara bakat, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para penggemar bahas\Nperubahan gaya yang tiba-tiba saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu, aku putuskan mewarnai rambutku\Nkebalikan dari kepribadianku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak hari itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku yakinkan diriku jika aku berdiri\Ndi depan publik sebagai idola,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan tunjukkan persona Ikihara-ku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rambut merah muda ini\Nsudah jadi ciri khasmu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingat kali pertama kau muncul\Ndengan warna rambut ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua penonton langsung jatuh cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya merah muda itu warna cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan tak tahu apa itu cinta,\Ndan aku datang untuk mencarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ironis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sebenarnya tak berhubungan\Ndengan warna rambut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena kau bekerja keras\Nhingga menyentuh hati semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa dibilang rambutku adalah wujud asliku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, wujud aslimu adalah dewa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berbeda dari Ouri.\NAku sama sekali tak istimewa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan aku tak berguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya bisa bekerja keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat memikirkan orang-orang\Nyang masih bersedia mendukungku,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu benar-benar membuatku bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku ingin membuat\Nsemua orang sebahagia mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ingin semua orang tersenyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau kalian\Nmelihat sisi memalukanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin semua orang menyukaiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu seperti cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini hanya pendapat pribadiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini mirip halusinasi yang biasa kulihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kau tak memikirkan orang tertentu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin ini cinta untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kau sudah tahu jawabannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ingin seseorang bahagia,\Ningin mereka tersenyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaan itu adalah cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak benar-benar memahaminya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi setidaknya aku berharap di hatimu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}cinta terasa seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}usahamu juga lahir
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari cinta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ingin seseorang bahagia,\Ningin mereka tersenyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaan itu adalah cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kino…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Uta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}U…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan Nona Kinoshita, bukan Utage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Uta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini komprominya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa perasaan ini juga cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya terpengaruh permainan teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau berkhayal kita lebih dari teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya. Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hampir saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon terlalu serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia hampir hancurkan Bumi\Nkarena salah paham konyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kini aku merasa bisa menangkan babak kedua.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah sebagai penggemar atau pembantumu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan mendukungmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan lakukan yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, babak kedua tentang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa F/ACE dari F/ACE?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari mulai babak kedua\NPertarungan Posisi Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sangat berbeda dari pertarungan\Nsimulasi skenario di babak pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini, kalian akan bersaing\Ndengan tubuh kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ajangnya adalah perlombaan air.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Posisi pertama adalah Tamon Fukuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kecepatan dan karismamu mengejutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku maju sambil pikirkan pacar-pacarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon, apa arti perjalananmu\Nuntuk temukan cinta?
